org.jamsim.util
Class MRUSet<E>

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.AbstractListModel
      org.jamsim.util.MRUSet<E>
Type Parameters:
E - element type
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Set<E>, ListModel
public class MRUSet<E>
extends AbstractListModel
implements Set<E>

A bounded set ordered from the most recently added to the first added. Implements AbstractListModel so it can be used as the data model for Swing components (eg: menus).

Method Detail

add

public boolean add(E item)
Add the specified item to the head of the MRUSet. If the item already exists it will be repositioned at the head of the set. If capacity has been reached, items at the end of the MRUSet will be removed.
